<p>First&#8230;Social Security is NOT the problem, the Military is. Yes, Medicare &amp; Medicaid is going to need severe trimming because we have a for profit sick care system based on not preventing, but treating disease, but S.S. was money paid for a retirement supplement and is due the payees. </p>
